OL,3,C'It's scandalous': People forced to
OL,4,Cpay fees over counterfeit stamps
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has issued a warning about
OL,7,Fcounterfeit stamps after a spate of
OL,8,Fpeople being charged to receive
OL,9,Fletters sent using fakes, ITV News
OL,10,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,12,FThe is under pressure to launch an
OL,13,Finvestigation after several people
OL,14,Funwittingly sent post with counterfeit
OL,15,Fstamps, leading people receiving the
OL,16,Fletters to be wrongly fined.
OL,18,FPam James spoke to after she paid a #5
OL,19,Fpenalty to collect a letter that was
OL,20,Fsent with a stamp deemed to be forged.
