OL,3,C'It's scandalous': People forced to
OL,4,Cpay fees over counterfeit stamps
OL,6,F"They said it is counterfeit, without
OL,7,Fasking me to send the envelope to them
OL,8,Fand I just think it's scandalous. It's
OL,9,Fanother scandal."
OL,11,FMs James' friend insisted she only
OL,12,Fever bought stamps from the Post
OL,13,FOffice or other reputable high street
OL,14,Fretailers.
OL,16,FThe issue has emerged since the postal
OL,17,Fservice switched entirely to a new
OL,18,Fbarcoded system last July.
