OL,3,C'It's scandalous': People forced to
OL,4,Cpay fees over counterfeit stamps
OL,6,FIsabella Tee, and her fiancee sent out
OL,7,Fwedding announcements with stamps
OL,8,Fbought from Amazon, which they
OL,9,Fbelieved to be genuine, but they
OL,10,Fturned out to be fakes.
OL,12,FBut some of the letters managed to get
OL,13,Fthrough Royal Mail's checking system,
OL,14,Fwhile others were told to pay fees.
OL,16,F"I would like to see there is
OL,17,Fsomething being done about the fact
OL,18,Fthere is clearly a system that doesn't
OL,19,Fwork," she said.
