OL,3,C'It's scandalous': People forced to
OL,4,Cpay fees over counterfeit stamps
OL,6,F"Every barcode is unique which allows
OL,7,Fus to identify whether a stamp is
OL,8,Fgenuine or not, and whether they have
OL,9,Fbeen previously used.
OL,11,F"We want our customers to buy stamps
OL,12,Fwith confidence. We strongly recommend
OL,13,Fthat customers only purchase stamps
OL,14,Ffrom Post Offices and other reputable
OL,15,FHigh Street retailers, and not to buy
OL,16,Fstamps online ` unless from the
OL,17,Fofficial Royal Mail shop."
