OL,4,Cpay fees over counterfeit stamps
OL,6,F"Our website provides customers with
OL,7,Fguidance on how to spot counterfeit or
OL,8,Fused stamps and we urge customers to
OL,9,Freport any suspicious stamps to Royal
OL,10,FMail via our so that we can
OL,11,Finvestigate.
OL,13,F"We are working hard to remove
OL,14,Fcounterfeit stamps from circulation.
OL,15,FWe regularly monitor to detect
OL,16,Fsuspicious activity, such as sales of
OL,17,Fheavily discounted stamps and work
OL,18,Fclosely with retailers and law
OL,19,Fenforcement agencies to identify those
OL,20,Fwho produce counterfeit stamps.
